Ide Owodiong-Idemeko (a mụrụ n'ụbọchị 11 n'ọnwa Juun n'afọ 1968) bụ onye isi azụmahịa Naijiria, onye ndọrọ ndọrọ ọchịchị, onye bụbu ndị ọrụ nchịkwa ExxonMobil na Onye isi oche nke 1001+ Voices Initiative for People Empowerment Ọ bụ onye na-azọ ọkwa onye omeiwu nke 2019 PDP Akwa Ibom North-East senatorial candidate 2019 yana onye PDP na-achọ ọkwa Gọvanọ nke Akwa Ibom Steeti n'afọ 2023.
